title: Sweet Home Alabama: A dozen of Talladega's stories, secrets and surprises unlocked
text: Sweet Home Alabama: A dozen of Talladega's stories, secrets and surprises unlocked Thursday, 22 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) Talladega Superspeedway has long been a fan-favorite for its intense, white-knuckle racing that has produced high drama, and at times, hard impacts, too.
